      "description": "Corgi ETF Trust I - Corgi NBIS 2x Daily ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by Corgi Strategies, LLC. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of the Netherlands. For its equity portion, the fund invests directly and through derivatives in stocks of companies operating across artificial intelligence, cloud infrastructure and related services sectors. It invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalization. For its fixed income portion, the fund invests directly and through derivatives in cash and cash equivalents and U.S. Treasury bills. The fund uses derivatives such as swaps to create its portfolio. Corgi ETF Trust I - Corgi NBIS 2x Daily ETF is domiciled in the United States.",
